## 🔴 critical.must (即座修正必須)

### 1. Open Redirect 脆弱性 (signin.tsx:64-66)

**問題**: リダイレクト先の URL 検証が不十分で、フィッシング攻撃のベクターとなる可能性があります。

```typescript
// 現状 (危険)
const callbackUrl = router.query.callbackUrl as string | undefined;
location.href = callbackUrl ? decodeURIComponent(callbackUrl) : PAGE_INFO.TOP.href();
```

**修正案**:
```typescript
const validateRedirectUrl = (url: string): string => {
  if (!url.startsWith('/')) return '/';
  if (url.includes('../') || url.includes('..\\')) return '/';

  try {
    const parsedUrl = new URL(url, window.location.origin);
    if (parsedUrl.origin !== window.location.origin) return '/';
  } catch {
    return '/';
  }

  return url;
};

const callbackUrl = router.query.callbackUrl as string | undefined;
location.href = validateRedirectUrl(callbackUrl || '/');
```

